Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:11.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This day is going to be perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.25,0:00:16.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The kind of day of which I've dreamed since I was small
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:18.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Everypony will gather 'round
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:20.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Say I look lovely in my gown
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:25.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,What they don't know is that I have fooled them all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:29.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This day was going to be perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:33.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The kind of day of which I've dreamed since I was small
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.33,0:00:36.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But instead of having cake
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:38.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With all my friends to celebrate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:42.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,My wedding bells, they may not ring for me at all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:44.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I could care less about the dress
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:47.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I won't partake in any cake
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:50.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Vows? Well I'll be lying when I say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:53.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That through any kind of weather
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:55.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'll want us to be together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.42,0:00:59.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The truth is I don't care for him at all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:02.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No, I do not love the groom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:06.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,In my heart, there is no room
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:12.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But I still want him to be all mine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:14.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We must escape before it's too late
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:17.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Find a way to save the day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.33,0:01:20.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Hope? I'd be lying if I say~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.67,0:01:22.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That I don't fear that I may lose him
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:24.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To one who wants to use him
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:27.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Not care for, love, and cherish him each day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:31.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For I oh so love the groom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.58,0:01:35.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All my thoughts, he does consume
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:43.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shining Armor, I'll be there very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:54.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Finally, the moment has arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:58.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For me to be one lucky bride
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:00.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Oh, the wedding we won't make
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:02.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,He'll end up marrying a fake
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.08,0:02:05.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Shining Armor will be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.83,0:02:06.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Mine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:07.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All mine